Internationally recognised data management specialist, Redstor presented its solutions at the 2018 MyBroadband Cloud, Hosting, and Security Conference, which took place at the Gallagher Convention Centre in Midrand on 13 June. “We specialise mainly in data management, including backup solutions, data recovery, and archiving,” said Phillip De Bruyn, Product Management General Manager at Redstor. “Data management for us means that we get involved in disaster recovery and archiving as well – it’s not just about backup. It’s an all-inclusive, unified data management platform that we offer.” The MyBroadband Cloud Conference provides IT executives, managers, and business owners from various industries with a platform to interact and do business with South Africa’s top cloud and hosting providers. For more information, watch the video below of Redstor at the conference.  This article was published in partnership with Redstor.